{"CHTHONIAN":[{"def":"Designating, or pertaining to, gods or spirits of the underworld; esp.","pos":""}],"CHTHONIC":[{"def":"Pertaining to the earth; earthy; as, chthonic religions.","pos":""},{"def":"A disease characterized by an irresistible desire to eat earth, observed in some parts of the southern United States, the West Indies, etc.","pos":""}]}